<table width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <tr>
        <td style="background-color: #004f9f; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            Verify Your Email
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: left; color: #333;">
            <p>Hi,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering on <strong>AutoRiaClone</strong>. Please verify your email address to complete your registration.</p>
            <p>Your verification code is:</p>
            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; color: #004f9f;">{{verifyCode}}</p>
            <p>Alternatively, you can verify your email by clicking the button below:</p>
            <table width="100%" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <a href="https://autoriclone.com/verify?email={{email}}&code={{verifyCode}}"
                        style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #004f9f; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
                        Verify Email
                        </a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">If you did not sign up for AutoRiaClone, please ignore this email.</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
